window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Cultivation is all fun and games.</b></p> <p><b>Until someone kills Merlin.</b></p> <p>Apparently, the only logical response to this fairly important change to Arthurian lore is for me to be reincarnated into Dark Age Cornwall. But don't worry, I have an absolute understanding of feudal power dynamics, Qi cycling, and anti-Saxon spell flinging.</p> <p>Oh, I also lie a lot.</p> <p>There's just the smallest chance that our timeline is doomed.</p>"; 
